---
import Layout from '../../layouts/AdminLayout.astro';
---

<Layout title="静态资源测试">
  <div class="admin-container">
    <h2>静态资源访问测试</h2>
    <p>以下是一些已上传的图片，用于测试静态资源服务是否正常工作：</p>
    
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px;">
      <div>
        <h3>截图.jpg</h3>
        <img src="/assets/uploads/截图.jpg" alt="截图" style="max-width: 300px; height: auto;" onerror="console.error('截图.jpg 加载失败')">
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h3>截图3.jpg</h3>
        <img src="/assets/uploads/截图3.jpg" alt="截图3" style="max-width: 300px; height: auto;" onerror="console.error('截图3.jpg 加载失败')">
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h3>picture.jpg</h3>
        <img src="/assets/uploads/picture.jpg" alt="picture" style="max-width: 300px; height: auto;" onerror="console.error('picture.jpg 加载失败')">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>